title: WindowFX
description:
Family friendly (mostly) video loops with a Halloween or Christmas theme to be used on your TV or shown on the wall or windows to create some fun holiday effects. Used with the WindowFX or AtmosFear / AtmosFX projector or other projection device. Many very cool effects can be done with these. Full contents of 3 WindowFX collections. 2 Halloween and 1 Christmas. Also other content in 1080p HD including the hard to find werewolf movies. Movies come in both horizontal and vertical orientation. Each collection has 6 movies. All in MP4 format. Happy Howlidays from The Big Bad Wolf.
